E1MFAU.original: ~z~and rub elbows with you blue collar types on the wrong side of the West River.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~沦落到西河彼岸和你们这些蓝领打交道。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~That's the old me. I'm clean now. I'm off the meth, and all that shit.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~那是曾经的我。我现在清白了。已经把冰毒之类的都戒了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Jim, brother, what can I do you for?
~z~Johnny, baby. I heard Billy's back inside.
~z~He is busy serving the people and communities of this great state and nation.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~他正在为这一伟大国家的民众和社区努力奋斗。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Johnny, what's up? Some of the brothers, they're asking questions.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~Johnny，你好吗？有些兄弟开始好奇了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Not this time. You can kill yourself on your own. Goodbye, Ash.
~z~I just see you in my dreams, sugar.
~z~We're not doing nothing, Johnny. Nothing we ain't supposed to. I need you to meet him, is all.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我们啥都没干，Johnny。没做越界的事。只是我需要你来找他。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Important enough for me to come down from my Ivory tower,
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~重要到足以让我跌落象牙塔，

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Yeah, he's locked up for a time.
~z~Stop saying that. It's meaningless. You don't even know what the words mean.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~别说了，这样没有意义。你都不知道什么是爱。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Congressman Stubbs cannot come to the phone right now.
~z~I want you to come see Ray Boccino. He needs some help.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我想让你来找一下Ray Boccino。他需要帮助。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~That guinea? Jesus, what you doing with him?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~那个意呆？天哪，你在他那儿干嘛？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Next thing you're gonna tell me we're doing some shit kicking for the LCPD.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~下次你是不是要让我们替LCPD跑腿啊。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I need forty bucks. I need it real bad, baby.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我需要四十块。急着要的，宝贝。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Yeah, we haven't seen one another in a time.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~是啊，我们有段时间没见面了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~They might give you two a conjugal visit trailer if you ask the screws nice.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~肯去拜托狱警的话，你俩说不定还能来次夫妻探视。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~He's got the details. So long, brother.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~他那儿有具体信息。再见，兄弟。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~It's nothing like that. Come to Drusilla's in Little Italy.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~不是那样的。来小意大利的Drusilla's一趟。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Oh, spare me the lectures. This is important, Jonathan.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~噢，别耍嘴皮子了。这次是正事，Jonathan。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I told you keeping that lawyer around would have its uses.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我就跟你说留着那个律师早晚能派上用场。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~You're gonna have to get your own hands dirty, Stubbs.
~z~I guess I do need another crazy motherfucker telling me what to do now that Billy's back on the inside.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~现在Billy又进去了，我大概确实要再找一个疯子教我做事。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Same old bullshit, Johnny. Can you come and meet me on Aspdin over in Acter?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~还是老样子，Johnny。你能来Acter区的Aspdin路找我吗？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~What's up, Johnny? How you like having Billy back?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~怎么说，Johnny？你对Billy回归有什么感受？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~It's just opposite the Libertonian. Go pay him a visit, if you're still thinking about your brothers and not just your own ego, that is.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~那家店在自由城博物馆对面。如果你还把弟兄们放在心里，就给我过去找他。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Ha ha. It can't be any more screwed up than what the club's really like. I'll check it out when I'm next in the House.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~哈哈。总不能比帮会的实际情况还差吧。我下次回会所去看看。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~You ever think like you're the only sane person in this fucked up world?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~你会不会觉得自己是这个傻逼世界中唯一的正常人？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~And you ain't even asked Clay or Terry to help out on a job.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~结果你连差事都不找Clay和Terry帮忙。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Tom Stubbs is a proud patriot and a God-fearing man. He's anti choice and pro freedom.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~Tom Stubbs是一个自豪的爱国者，对上帝心存敬畏。他反对自由堕胎，支持自由。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I can't really talk. Just come over to my place, okay. Hurry, baby.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~说不来话，麻烦你过来找我，好吗？快点，宝贝。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Meet me at your Clubhouse. I drink single malt.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~来你们会所找我。我喝单一麦芽威士忌。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~This guy's at one of them dumb ass gentlemen's clubs in Algonquin - the kind without tits - The Jousters.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~这位议员现在在Algonquin的一家绅士俱乐部——不露奶的那种——枪斗士。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~As long as they can get the imported hairdryers they ride started, it'll work.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~只要他们的进口吹风机能打着火，就行了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~The pay will be more than adequate.
~z~Johnny boy? John. I need some help.
~z~Johnny. You coming here or what, sugar?
~z~Check out the Deadbeats' website. I've sent you a link.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~看看死妈天使的网站吧。链接发你邮箱了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I'm not in the mood to do any killing for the supposed elite today.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我今天没心情替二代人上人杀人。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~If you're interested in helping me out with this, you can call me and I'll tell you what I need.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~如果有兴趣帮我的忙，你就联系我，我会告诉你要求。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Liz Torres needs a hand with something, I told her you'd be down for it.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~Liz Torres需要一个帮手，我跟她推荐了你。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Come on, Ash, give it up. You seriously got time to dream in between your three day ice binges?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~得了吧，Ash，别扯了。你溜了三天冰，哪有工夫做梦啊。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I mean, when Billy was head of the chapter Brian was doin' his laundry and packing his bongs for him.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~以前Billy当分会老大的时候，Brian又给他洗衣服又给他点烟。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Please continue to donate generously to his re-election campaign. God bless America.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~请您继续捐款支持他的连任竞选。天佑美利坚。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I'm hanging around with a reprobate like yourself and my old lady prefers the pipe to me.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我天天跟你这种恶棍在一块，老娘们比起我更喜欢吸毒。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~He loves democracy and wants to reform the government. He will serve you well.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~他热爱民主，想要改革政府。他将为民服务。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I ain't got a hand-out for ya. Sorry.
~z~If it isn't my white knight. My saviour. Johnny K.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~这不是我的白衣骑士、我的救星，Johnny K吗。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~We are moving up in the world, Johnny.
~z~You should see what the world thinks of The Lost MC, man. Some asshole put up a website for us. I've sent you a link.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~你应该看下世人对失落帮的想法，兄弟。有混蛋给我们建了网站，链接我发你了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Ha ha. I'll look at it on the house computer. So long, brother.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~哈哈。我会用会所的电脑看的。再见，兄弟。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~The amount of help I need from a man with your skills has tripled in volume, and that's a conservative estimate.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我需要你这种能人帮的忙已经多了两倍了，这还是保守估计。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~They gonna be able to handle themselves?
~z~Okay, man. I'll give one of the boys a call. Get 'em to come along on the next run. Thanks, Jim.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~好的，兄弟。我会找他们的。下次一定叫上。谢了，Jim。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Once you go down the dark path, it just keeps goin', don't it, Stubbs?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~一朝走错路，没有回头路，不是吗，Stubbs？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I ain't your saviour, baby. I might have beaten up a few pimps and pushers.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我不是你的救星，宝贝。我确实收拾了几个拉皮条的和毒贩子。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Didn't think I'd hear from you again.
~z~There's a Congressman, needs your help, Tom Stubbs III.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~有一个众议员需要你的帮助，Tom Stubbs三世。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I sent them guys, Malc and DeSean, over to her place in South Bohan as well.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我也让Malc和DeSean过去了，去她在South Bohan的住处。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I need a knight in shining armor to take me away from this mess. They're gonna kill me... or worse.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~需要一个披坚执锐的骑士救我出去。他们要杀我...甚至更糟。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~A hand-out ain't gonna fix it, Johnny boy. I'm into something bad.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~光救济也没有用，Johnny仔。我现在的情况很糟。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Oh, I think so. Don't really know where the other brothers stand, so it's them or no one.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~呃，不至于。主要还是帮里弟兄各怀鬼胎，只能找他们了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Now listen, Klebitz. The tax payer is picking up the bill for this call so I'm going to make it brief.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~你听好，Klebitz。打这通电话用的是纳税人的钱，我就长话短说了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I'm here. What can I do you for, Congressman?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~是我。有什么我能帮忙的，议员？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Some project on Wardite. Come quick, baby.
~z~I'll call if I feel the need to keep you in the lifestyle to which you're accustomed.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~哪天想帮你维系锦衣玉食的生活方式了，我再联系你。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~But I'm never gonna save you from yourself. I learned that a long time ago.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~但我不可能帮你救赎自己。这我早就明白了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~If you ever feel like this war we're in ain't worth it, that'll persuade you it is.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~要是你觉得开战不值得，看完网站就不会这么想了。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~You interested in procuring them for him?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~你有兴趣替他入手这些摩托吗？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Yeah, I heard. Look, Johnny. Look, have you got any money?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~嗯，听说了。听着，Johnny。那个，你身上有钱吗？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~These guys wanna help out, man. Out of respect.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~他们很想帮你的，兄弟。出于尊敬。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~As long as it ain't gonna get us in the shit with any more dirty cops.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~别害我们再被臭条子盯上就行。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Didn't seem like that when I last saw you. Just checking you're okay. Bye, Ash.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我上次见到你的时候可不是这样。你没事就好。再见，Ash。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I need you to meet a friend of mine - Ray Boccino.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我需要你来见一下我的朋友，Ray Boccino。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Fuck you, Johnny. Why you being like that? I just like Billy, that's all.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~操你妈的，Johnny。说这种话干嘛？我只是喜欢Billy，仅此而已。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Them cops ain't around no more. Get Angus on the wire when you're ready to roll.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~那些条子早就不在了。准备好了就给Angus打个电话。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Listen, that guy we stole those Angels of Death bikes for, he's got a whole shoppin' list of bikes he wants.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~听着，之前让我们偷死亡天使摩托的那个人，他想要的摩托还有很多。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I like it fine. Look, I got to go. Take care of yourself.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我无所谓。听着，我要挂了。你多保重。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~We're over at Drusilla's in Little Italy. Can't wait to see you, baby.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我们在小意大利的Drusilla's。期待你的到来，宝贝。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~I didn't think I'd call you. You hear about Billy?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~我也没想到啊。听说Billy的事了吗？

E1MFAU.original: ~z~Hey, Johnny boy. It's nothing. I mean it's something, but, but, it ain't like you think.
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~嘿，Johnny仔。没怎么，不是，确实有点事，但不是你想的那样。

E1MFAU.original: ~z~You like a lot of people, Ash.
~z~Politicians and lawyers? What are we becoming, man?
E1MFAU.translated: ~z~政客跟律师？我们都成什么了，老兄？
